Ranger Help for: make rope
===========================

SYNTAX:      rope
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   3
BASE SP:     15
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to craft rope from natural materials such
as vines and grasses. Rope is an essential component in several other
crafting skills, including making tents, bows, and fish traps. The
Ranger must have suitable materials in their inventory. The quality
and length of the rope depends on the materials used and the Ranger's
crafting proficiency.
